title: Australia-The Story Of Us - Season 1
description:
Australia-The Story Of Us - Season 1

An extraordinary narrative more than 40,000 years in the making about the people, places and events which have shaped our nation from the first footprints on our continent to the present day.

Ep 1 - Worlds Collide
Ep 2 - Breakout
Ep 3 - Fair Go
Ep 4 - New Nation At War
Ep 5 - Hard Roads To Glory
Ep 6 - Nation Building
Ep 7 - Revolution
Ep 8 - New Frontiers
